# --- Images / binaries: repo is TEXT-ONLY (binary policy, 2026-06-29) ---
# Guide photos live in a per-guide folder on the owner's desktop, never in the
# repo. The publish kit reads images from the local drop folder at publish time.
# Keeps drop folders (e.g. guide-kit/guides/<slug>/images/) out of git.
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.png
*.gif
*.webp
*.heic
*.heif
*.avif
*.tif
*.tiff
*.bmp
*.ico
*.psd
